### ============================================
### Tenant Theme Module (US-4.4)
### ============================================
### Multi-tenant theming with dynamic color customization
### Scalar Docs: {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

### -----------------------------------------
### Step 1: Login first to get auth token
### -----------------------------------------
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.corelio.app",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### -----------------------------------------
### Theme Read Operations
### -----------------------------------------

### Get current tenant's theme configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme/current
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### -----------------------------------------
### Theme Update Operations
### -----------------------------------------

### Enable custom theme - Orange
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primaryColor": "#FF5722",
  "useCustomTheme": true
}

