### -----------------------------------------
### Validation Error Cases
### -----------------------------------------

### Invalid hex color format (should return 400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primaryColor": "not-a-color",
  "useCustomTheme": true
}

###

### Invalid hex color - missing # prefix (should return 400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primaryColor": "FF5722",
  "useCustomTheme": true
}

###

### Invalid hex color - wrong length (should return 400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primaryColor": "#FFF",
  "useCustomTheme": true
}

###

### Unauthorized - no token (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/theme/current
